Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:01.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:08.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:11.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the time he was little,\NMiroku has had no close kin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:20.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was taught everything,\nboth good and bad, by one man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:24.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, Monk Mushin was about to\npreside over one last feast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:12.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serial murders at\npopular temples?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:49.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lately, highly spiritual monks\nand head priests have been murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:52.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Monks and priests?\NWhat significance does that have?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not the one to {\i1}ask....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a terrible story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But does it have anything to do\nwith the remaining Sacred Jewel shards?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:04.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would that Naraku go so far as\nto kill ordinary humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then it's got nothing to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:13.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, there aren't any highly\nspiritual monks among us, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey {\i1}you....{\i0} That isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:23.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:25.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}That's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Hachiemon, the Raccoon Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin is going to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's regrettable, but I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mushin is the monk who\nraised you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's who we went to see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:46.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to treat your Wind Tunnel,\nright, Miroku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NTell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....for{\i0} the past few days, I've been\nstaying at Master Mushin's temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hyee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:26.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And that's why I rushed\nover to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems that Hachi\nwas not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You shall die sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:14.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did Hachi speak the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:19.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hachi said that you\nare going to die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:28.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am going to die very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:40.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the path I've chosen.\NI have no complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:45.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm glad I got to see you\none more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! We all eventually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No sense getting sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, Inuyasha is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All living things eventually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:33.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But isn't there something\nwe can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I dozed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Mushin is going to die...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um, Master {\i1}Mushin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything you'd\nlike to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything I'd like to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She means you'd better take care\nof any unfinished business
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,before you go\nto the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, that's what she means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:18.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, let's {\i1}see....{\i0}\NI'd like to drink {\i1}sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're already drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}then....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, you can clean up\nthe temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}First?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:42.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:47.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do I....have {\i1}to....do{\i0} this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the way to go, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, this is the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But cleaning this huge temple\nis a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:08:00.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wind Tunnel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he could use the\NWind Tunnel freely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:11.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! The dirt on the {\i1}floor....{\i0}\nthe trash in the {\i1}bedrooms....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:20.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With my Wind Tunnel, you don't\nneed to use a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See? Spic and span in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:24.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The suction power is so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotta hand it to Miroku, the\NHuman Vacuum Cleaner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't say it out loud,\nbut I sure would like to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, you can air out\nthe beddings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh! Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Why me?! Why me?! Why me?!\N- Not so hard, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:53.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Tetsusaiga! Tetsusaiga! Tetsusaiga!\N- He's really into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:55.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the type who can't\nsit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, cut the grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:05.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- And that's it.\N- All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:25.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We cleaned the temple,\naired out the beddings,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and did all the wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we prepare dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This {\i1}is....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's an {\i1}inn....{\i0}\nand obviously expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to drink\nto my heart's content in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you, depraved monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You really are going to die,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course! Would I ask for these\nthings if I weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:00.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well anyway, come on,\nlet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:02.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} his last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh come on....snuggle up closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:16.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} his last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cleaning, {\i1}washing....{\i0}\nthen a feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing special, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:34.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he's just a drunk monk,\nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the speed of\na country monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin, isn't there\nanything else you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:48.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well....{\i0} I want to drink {\i1}sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're already drinking!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:52.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}sake{\i0} I desire is\nno ordinary {\i1}sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what kind of {\i1}sake{\i0} is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The legendary {\i1}sake,{\i0} the Mist of Sages!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mist of Sages?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Beyond four mountains from here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there is a sacred peak known\nas Kasumidake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:15.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A sage who lives there makes a\nvery rare {\i1}sake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and that is known as\nthe Mist of Sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:21.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those who drink this {\i1}sake{\i0} feel\nas though they have climbed into Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:26.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Its taste is indescribably delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you want us to acquire\nsome of this {\i1}sake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:33.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not finished\nwith the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A countless many have set out to\nacquire the {\i1}sake,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:42.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but not one has ever\nreturned with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I could drink this {\i1}sake,{\i0}\NI would have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:49.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:50.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:53.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll go for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:58.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You said, if you drink it,\nyou would have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're such a great guy, Miroku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so are you, Inuyasha,\nsince you are coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! I'm {\i1}just....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:20.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:29.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, that is Kasumidake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, we just have to\nfind this sage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and have him share\nsome of his {\i1}sake{\i0} with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:45.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just hope he's willing\nto share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:58.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know. I sense it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the aura of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This mist... what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:33.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:51.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm Kagome Higurashi\nand I'm going to sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:54.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next, I, Kagome Higurashi,\nwill now dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Number Three,\NKagome Higurashi will laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It looks like there are\na bunch of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, let's sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, don't inhale the mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the work of the demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:22.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know just what it is exactly,\nbut it makes one intoxicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:25.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So do not inhale, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too late!\NThe others are already drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I meant the rest of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, one more song!\NKagome Higurashi, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Calm down, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:44.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sango, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget {\i1}'im....{\i0} Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That flirtatious {\i1}monk....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and Kagome... huh?\NThere's so many of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But let's just leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, just the two of {\i1}us....{\i0}\NLet's go defeat Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.70,0:15:14.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit! Sit! Sit!\NSit! Sit! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now she's crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:33.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh....{\i0} The one who made her cry\nis going to console her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, you flirting cheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now she's angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this what the demon intends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To intoxicate us with his demonic\npower and make us fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha! Scatter the mist\nwith your Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Sit. Sit. Sit. Sit. Sit. Sit. Sit. Sit.\N- L-Look b-before y-you s-speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:58.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:02.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,At this {\i1}rate....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no {\i1}choice....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:10.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not manly to fear being\npoisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One must drink {\i1}sake,{\i0}\nbut not get drunk on {\i1}sake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:29.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the {\i1}sake{\i0} sages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:42.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:49.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm out of {\i1}sake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All gone already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ohh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:08.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is superb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miroku....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:23.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been quite a while since\nwe sat and talked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:25.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me go, Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:36.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I do, you will also be sucked\ninto your father's Wind Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess it will bother you\neven if I tell you not to let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Mushin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is still alive, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The uncertainty of tomorrow\ncan only be understood
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,by those who don't know if\nthey will live another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:16.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until Naraku is defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:20.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you are not able to forget any of this\neven when drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I may not be able to forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I can get drunk with the hope\nof defeating Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:37.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Mushin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin....Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:56.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:18:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Mushin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:09.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you're not dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.48,0:19:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What....?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does this mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\N"what does this mean"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So....because all those high-ranking\nmonks and priests were being killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:35.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you figured you were going to\nbe murdered, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:36.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong\nwith your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool! I'm perfectly healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:47.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then what about the blood\NHachi saw you spit up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}that....{\i0} A piece of fish got\nstuck in the wrong pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No {\i1}way....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:00.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-This is so {\i1}stupid....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:04.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who else around here\nis highly spiritual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The next victim is sure to {\i1}be....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Believe us, you are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What did I say wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! Didn't I tell you\nnot to bother with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll {\i1}say....{\i0} What a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:28.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:37.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I just thought something\nlike this is nice sometimes. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is this kid up to anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:31.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Half-killing so many highly spiritual\nmonks and priests...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he looking into their hearts?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, I'm done.\NFinish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:41.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't see anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if they're highly spiritual,\nthey're mere humans, that's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you trying to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The border between\nthis world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:57.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where the final shard\nof the Sacred Jewel lies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:47.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mysterious happenings occur\nnight after night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.58,0:23:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Only the wealthy are targeted
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and no matter how tight\nthe security,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.69,0:23:54.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the homes are broken into and\nvaluables are stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:57.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too strange for it to be the\nwork of robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:59.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon which can make\nitself disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will they be able to work together\nto slay the demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"A Strange, Invisible Demon Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:10.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.14,0:24:11.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll slay it for sure!
